      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and represents a rare find for any serious buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original factory luster with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is equally pristine; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, and all electronic features and climate controls function perfectly. It has been meticulously garaged and serviced ahead of schedule, with full documentation available. This is a collector-quality car that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
