    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s still got plenty of life left? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in such solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a charm\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s got that 'ready-to-go' feel, and I\u2019ve taken great care of it. Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself why I've loved driving it so much!",
