    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a recent double-VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing and engine response. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. While the exterior reflects honest use, the mechanical vitals are robust, featuring a recent rod bearing replacement and a complete cooling system refresh. The suspension maintains excellent kinematic integrity, making this a mechanically sound platform for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
