    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium upholstery is intact with only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every button and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is a standout. It has been strictly maintained with a documented service history, ensuring the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. If you are looking for a dependable, attractive vehicle that has been cared for by a detail-oriented owner, this is the one. It is road-ready with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 32500.0,
