      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a standard of care and mechanical integrity that distinguishes it within its class. This automobile offers a refined driving experience, supported by a documented history of consistent upkeep. Both the interior and exterior remain in commendable order, ensuring aesthetic appeal and continued reliability. A sophisticated acquisition for the discerning driver who prioritizes quality and proven performance.",
