    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs super smoothly, and is just waiting for a new home. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love how it drives!",
