    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, a high-revving masterpiece utilizing eight individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS steplessly variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal longitudinal and lateral traction. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and aluminum-intensive suspension components. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement with treated shells and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the 8,400 RPM redline is explored with confidence. The hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering provides exceptional feedback, unencumbered by modern electronic assistance. A mechanically robust example of the final naturally aspirated M-car.",
